// Template for local, per-machine overrides.
//
// Setup:
//   cp Apps/Config/Signing.local.xcconfig.example Apps/Config/Signing.local.xcconfig
//   # then fill in LOCAL_DEVELOPMENT_TEAM below with your 10-character
//   # Apple Developer Team ID (developer.apple.com → Membership → Team ID).
//
// `Signing.local.xcconfig` is gitignored. The committed `Signing.xcconfig`
// includes it via `#include?` (after the public defaults in
// `Distribution.xcconfig`), so any value you set here overrides the
// committed default and keeps personal/infra values out of every
// generated pbxproj and Info.plist.

// Required for signed local builds (left blank = unsigned-only builds).
LOCAL_DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =

// Optional: crash-report contact address for YOUR builds. Leave unset to
// ship the neutral "no contact configured" default. Forks set their own.
// LOCAL_CONTACT_EMAIL = you@example.com

// Optional: override the Sparkle auto-update appcast feed (macOS) for
// YOUR builds (e.g. a privately-served feed). The committed default is a
// GitHub Releases-hosted appcast. NOTE: xcconfig treats `//` as a comment,
// so build the scheme separator from $(SLASH) (defined in Distribution.xcconfig):
// LOCAL_SU_FEED_URL = https:$(SLASH)$(SLASH)example.com/appcast.xml
